OL,4,G2000FCasualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,5,     GThe pace at Barnsley Casualty is
OL,6,     Grelentless; other hospitals in
OL,7,     Gthe area are full and as a
OL,8,     Gresult, ambulances are being
OL,9,     Gdiverted to Barnsley.
OL,10,G2100FA&E: Crash Scene Emergency
OL,11,     GRich, 17, goes flying after
OL,12,     Ghitting a roadblock on his
OL,13,     Gmountain bike. Can surgeons do
OL,14,     Genough to ensure he doesn't
OL,15,     Gsustain lasting brain injury due
OL,16,     Gto his open skull fracture?
OL,17,G2200F999: Critical Condition
OL,18,     GMotorcyclist Danny is rushed into
OL,19,     Gthe emergency department
OL,20,     Gfollowing a high-speed road
OL,21,     Gtraffic accident in north Wales.
